Mix HTML
===================

Menggabung Kode PHP dengan HTML :

<?php 
$nama	="Siswa Codepolitan"; 
$alamat	="Bandung";
?>
<html>
<body>
<h1>Selamat Datang</h1><br>
<?php echo $nama; ?><br>
Alamat: <?php echo $alamat; ?>
</body>
</html>

=========================================
Menyisipkan Kode HTML didalam kode PHP
==========================================

<?php 
$nama	="<h2>Siswa Codepolitan</h2>"; 
$alamat	="<h2>Bandung</h2>";
?>
<html>
<body>
<h1>Selamat Datang</h1><br>
<?php echo $nama; ?><br>
<?php echo $alamat; ?>
</body>
</html>
